Hmâna: [[{{#Special:Redirect}}/file/Example.jpg]], [[{{#Special:Redirect}}/page/64308]], [[{{#Special:Redirect}}/revision/328429]], [[{{#Special:Redirect}}/user/101]], or [[{{#Special:Redirect}}/logid/186]].
logentry-delete-revision: $1 {{GENDER:$2|changed}} visibility of {{PLURAL:$5|a revision|$5 revisions}} on page $3: $4
logentry-move-move-noredirect: $1 {{GENDER:$2|moved}} page $3 to $4 without leaving a redirect
logentry-move-move_redir: $1 ta châhmia $3 tawh $4 lâta a {{GENDER:$2|paly haw}}
logentry-patrol-patrol-auto: $1 cha $4 eih châhmia $3 kha anotata {{GENDER:$2|abina a sa}}
